descriptionHtml:
AYLA has it's own world space.

Entrance to AYLA "Portal Gem Door" is located at WHITERUN, go over the draw bridge then turn left into the passage,see picture for more info.

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

[b]Cleaned[/b] with TES5Edit.

[b]Requirements:[/b] Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.[b]Installation:[/b] Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it                             manually,  then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[b]Unistallation:[/b]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.

[b]CREDITS:[/b] Many thanks to arrioch for his permission to use his, "Arri's Snow Elf Ruins Retexture"
               Also a very big thank you to, "Varlaisaran for his Adabala Building System - Ayleid Transfusion"
               Thank you to Tamira for his, "New Plants 1_3 Modders Resources"
               And last but by no means least, "Malo Statues by Malo"



 My Regards to you all.

Thank You.
